title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Dhaka · ★New · 3 bedrooms · 3 beds · 3 baths
listing_description: This 2,200 sqft three bedroom three bathroom unit preserves the atmosphere of a traditional Bengali house while providing you with every modern comfort. The rental unit is a completely serviced apartment in the heart of Dhaka City allowing you to enjoy this vibrant city without any household worries. The apartment is close to Dhanmondi Lake, Bashundhara Shopping Centre, and many famous restaurants. The central location also ensures easy transport to most major attractions available in Dhaka.

listing_description:
This stylish place to stay is perfect for group trips in the old residential area of Dhaka city. The property has 60% open space and single unit house in 0.35 Acre Land. Within 150meter the renowned Dhanmondi Lake will be found which is perfect for walking and spending quality time. The property has Central Airconditioning system with fresh filtered chilled air, 100% RO treated water in Tap and hot water facilities. 

The two level terrace will give the best environment for being refreshed.
